
[1]whoredom

   WHOREDOM, n. Horedom.

   1. Lewdness; fornication; practice of unlawful commerce with the other
   sex. It is applied to either sex, and to any kind of illicit commerce.

   2. In Scripture, idolatry; the desertion of the worship of the true
   God, for the worship of idols.
